{"tid":854298,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"老貓請入！唔使做有錢收好介紹","createTime":"2018-10-09T09:10:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T09:31:13.000Z","uid":54870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e0b4e240b408fe5301785e5607b7892ed0f9d0a3","tid":854298,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:10:25.000Z","msg":"【招募臨床研究志願者】<br />\n<br />\n&bull; 香港中文大學一期臨床研究中心現正招募健康人仕參與一項稱為 RO7020531 之藥物的研究（也稱為臨床試驗）。RO7020531 被研究用於用於乙型肝炎病毒所引致的肝臟疾病的治療。<br />\n<br />\n&bull; 招募對象: 18-60歲的男性及女性，甄選檢查證明健康狀況良好。<br />\n<br />\n&bull; 參與研究你要做些什麼: 到研究中心進行健康檢查、服食研究藥物、留院(15日14夜)觀察及覆診(1次)。如有需要，您可能被邀請進行額外的覆診。<br />\n<br />\n&bull; 研究補償: 您將會在完成研究後獲得港幣 $31,500 的現金津貼，以補助您因參與本研究所付出的時間、所造成的不便或因參與本研究而付出的合理開支。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.p1ctc.med.cuhk.edu.hk/Apps/VolunteerTC2.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.p1ctc.med.cuhk.edu.hk%2FApps%2FVolunteerTC2.aspx&d=aZ%2BvH1YulBJsRS0Mk%2FwPpkjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=1f3585ef\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.p1ctc.med.cuhk.edu.hk/Apps/VolunteerTC2.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"96bdee09e3ed8b78231243b6917be9379055d45b","tid":854298,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:11:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2177803/%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E8%87%A8%E5%BA%8A%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%833%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E8%81%98%E3%80%8C%E4%BA%BA%E8%82%89%E8%A9%A6%E8%97%A5%E5%93%A1%E3%80%8D%E3%80%80%E7%95%99%E9%99%A215%E5%A4%A9%E6%88%96%E5%98%94%E5%90%90%E6%B5%81%E9%BC%BB%E8%A1%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2177803%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2587%25A8%25E5%25BA%258A%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%25833%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583%25E8%2581%2598%25E3%2580%258C%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2582%2589%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E8%2597%25A5%25E5%2593%25A1%25E3%2580%258D%25E3%2580%2580%25E7%2595%2599%25E9%2599%25A215%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%2588%2596%25E5%2598%259